<!--> In this view, we are using the Rails `form_with` helper to generate an HTML
form to create products. This helper uses a form builder to handle things like 
CSRF tokens, generating the URL based upon the model: provided, and even tailoring
the submit button text to the model.<-->

<h1>New product</h1>

<%= form_with model: @product do |form| %>
    <div>
        <%= form.label :name %>
        <%= form.text_field :name %>
    </div>

    <div>
        <%= form.submit %>
    </div>
<% end %>